reviewText: You can see these for free on YouTube, but for adventure fly fishermen it's a great take-along to inspire and entertain while on a trip of your own.
FAST QICKFIRE EDITING GETS A BIT FRUSTRATING TO WATCH AFTER A WHILE
if you liked Geofish, you'll dig this offering from the fellas.

This whole series is a must-see! Edge-of-your-seat reality/adventure show starring four wild anglers traveling all across the world in search of some of the most elusive fish on the planet! Five stars, recommend!
